 Well, there ARE some solutions available in the PC sector.

 But most don't follow the IFF specifications in all parts
 (done differently than e.g. an Amiga programmer would do it ;-)
 or lack the ability of handling uncompressed IFF graphics,
 24 bit IFF-ILBMs or HAM6/HAM8.

